# Vendored Real-ESRGAN upscaler (binary + weights, ~76MB, re-downloadable — see docs/upscaling.md)
tools/realesrgan/

# Generated & large media — regenerable. Git tracks the pipeline (code, prompts,
# storyboards, docs), not its heavy outputs. Hand-curated INPUT media stays tracked:
#   projects/*/references/  = accuracy-gate ground truth (small, curated, hard to reproduce)
#   assets/style_anchors/   = brand look anchors
*.mp4
*.mov
*.webm
*.mkv
*.avi
projects/*/images/
projects/*/images_4k/
projects/*/clips/
projects/*/videos/
projects/*/review/
